5. STANDARD OPERATING CYCLE (SOC)

This is the universal loop all cognitive exoskeletons run on.

1. Intent Setting

Operator defines goal or problem.

2. Scaffolding Deployment

Symbols, roles, or frameworks invoked.

3. Machine Amplification

AI generates structure, expansion, and organization.

4. Operator Correction

Human prunes, steers, and directs.

5. Iteration

